claim: Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older
explanation: The image is a portion of the full prescribing information for Flublok. In the “Indications and Usage” section it states: “Flublok is a vaccine indicated for active immunization … Flublok approved for use in persons 18 years of age and older.” This explicit statement directly supports the claim that Flublok is approved for adults 18 years and older.
